		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Sauron&#39;s Anti-Ranger Task Force Part 2</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='77' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/lotr/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='25'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(3.83)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=24615&PHPSESSID=0f944c0585dfb3fafb2b7d724583feda">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=10894">Alex "Worlds" Weavers</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=10894&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> They&#39;re Back.  The Dwarves don&#39;t suck, and the orcs kill everything.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> July 26, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> -.[Sites].-<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(201)">East Road</a>*-.<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(214)">Trollshaw Forest</a>*-.<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(217)">Council Courtyard</a>*-.<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(226)">Moria Stairway</a>*-.<br />
  .-*Taco Bell*-.<br />
  .-*Galadriel&#39;s Gale*-.<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(232)">Anduin Confluence</a>*-.<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(238)">Shores of Nen Hithoel</a>*-.<br />
  .-*<a href="javascript:card_browser(242)">Summit of Amon Hen</a>*-.<br />
<br />
-.[Starting].-<br />
  Frodo, Yajibijah<br />
  <a href="javascript:card_browser(96)">The One Ring, Isildur&#39;s Bane</a><br />
  <a href="javascript:card_browser(35)">Gimli, Son of Gloin</a><br />
  Gloin, Father of Gimli<br />
<br />
-.[Free Peoples Forces].- 28 + 2 Starters<br />
  Fror x2<br />
  Farin x2<br />
  Book of Mazarbul<br />
  <a href="javascript:card_browser(309)">Dwarven Axe</a> x4<br />
  Mines of Khazad-Dum<br />
  <a href="javascript:card_browser(139)">Stairs of Khazad-dum</a> x4<br />
  <a href="javascript:card_browser(910)">Till Durin Wakes Again</a><br />
  <a href="javascript:card_browser(55)">Gimli&#39;s Helm</a><br />
